===Etymology===
From {{He.}} '''עֵשָׂו'''

===Proper noun===
'''Esau'''
# (''Bible'') The son of [[Isaac]] and [[Rebekah]] and the older twin brother of [[Jacob]] in the [[biblical]] book of [[Genesis]].

